The paper deals with image-to-image translation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of a generator network, which is a common technique in deep learning and machine learning (cs.LG). The method also involves the use of a latent variable, which is a common technique in generative models and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of an attention mechanism, which is a common technique in computer graphics and visualization (cs.GR). Finally, the paper deals with datasets beyond faces, which could potentially fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
